Email Template Slicer
======================

An Email Template Slicer that helps create custom layouts for marketing emails.

Up to date functionality
======================== 
	The user can provide a url for the image in the textbox and click submit to 
	render the image onto the slicing area. When the user right clicks on any 
	point in the slicing area, a horizontal line is drawn at that point.

Note
=====
	paper.js has some issues with chrome where it doesn't work when if you try to run it locally.
	You can use a webserver program like mongoose to set up a webserver and run it from
	there. You can also use firefox to run it locally on your machine. 